                           XSS REFLECTED (CUSTOME_HEADER) 

  * Open your burpsuite then, intercept the request

  * IN burpsuite : you put Header :
  bWAPP : "Done" <=== You can put any thing , then you forward the request .

  *Turn off the intercept of the burpsuite . 

  *Go to the page and reload the page . 

  *You can see the name we put  in the custome header we write bWAPP is shown beside it . 

  * Go pack to the burpsuite , the let's put the payload 
  bWAPP : <script>alert('Done')</script> 

  *Now go and use any other payloads .

